Key Match Events: Abdel Samad Ezzalzouli opened the scoring for the national team in the 18th minute
Azzedine Ounahi scored a stunning strike from outside the box in the 38th minute
Ounahi scored his second and Morocco’s third goal just two minutes into first-half stoppage time
Achraf Hakimi scored in the 45th minute
Soufiane Rahimi converted a penalty in the 71st minute to make it 5-0 for Morocco
Post-Match Reflections: Morocco maintains their position at the top of Group B
Regragui aims to improve the national team’s overall performance
The team’s struggles, particularly against opponents employing a deep defensive block, have drawn significant criticism of Regragui and his squad
Miscellaneous Highlights: Yassine Bounou, Morocco’s goalkeeper, exited the match due to a hamstring strain
The match was officiated by Gambian referee Bakary Gassama, assisted by Abdoulie Bojang Jallow and Nfally Jarju, with Omar Salah as the fourth official
